WEBVTT

00:01.435 --> 00:01.801
Messi.

00:06.744 --> 00:07.575
My hero.

00:10.593 --> 00:11.484
My idol.

00:13.648 --> 00:14.645
You're legendary.

00:16.779 --> 00:17.623
Unstoppable.

00:26.034 --> 00:27.113
The best ever.

00:31.693 --> 00:33.288
I've always wanted to be like you.

00:33.993 --> 00:35.162
To play like you.

00:35.969 --> 00:37.763
But I am not you.

00:39.719 --> 00:41.484
I want to see what the world thinks of me.

00:42.463 --> 00:43.716
And what I can create.

